{"id":113,"parent_id":93,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":113,"title":"Leviticus 20","subtitle":"","short_title":"Lev.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 20"],[".studySummary",["i","The death penalty is prescribed for sacrificing children to Molech, cursing father and mother, adultery, homosexual behavior, bestiality, spiritualism, and other abominations—Various laws and ordinances are listed."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.1","order":"02.04.020.10413"},["b","1"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto Moses, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.2","order":"02.04.020.10414"},["b","2"],"Again, thou shalt say to the children of Israel, Whosoever",["i","he be"],"of the children of Israel, or of the strangers that sojourn in Israel, that giveth",["i","any"],"of his seed unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Molech"],"; he shall surely be put to death: the people of the land shall stone him with stones."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.3","order":"02.04.020.10415"},["b","3"],"And I will set my face against that man, and will cut him off from among his people; because he hath given of his seed unto Molech, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"defile"],"my sanctuary, and to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"profane"],"my holy name."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.4","order":"02.04.020.10416"},["b","4"],"And if the people of the land do any ways hide their eyes from the man, when he giveth of his seed unto Molech, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"kill"],"him not:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.5","order":"02.04.020.10417"},["b","5"],"Then I will set my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"face"],"against that man, and against his family, and will cut him off, and all that go a whoring after him, to commit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"whoredom"],"with Molech, from among their people."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6","order":"02.04.020.10418"},["b","6"],"¶And the soul that turneth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"after"],"such as have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"familiar"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"spirits"],", and after",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"wizards"],", to go a whoring after them, I will even set my face against that soul, and will",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"cut him off"],"from among his people."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.7","order":"02.04.020.10419"},["b","7"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Sanctify"],"yourselves therefore, and be ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"holy"],": for I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.8","order":"02.04.020.10420"},["b","8"],"And ye shall keep my statutes, and do them: I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Lord"]],"which sanctify you."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.9","order":"02.04.020.10421"},["b","9"],"¶For every one that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"curseth"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"father"],"or his mother shall be surely put to death: he hath cursed his father or his mother; his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"blood"],["i","shall be"],"upon him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10","order":"02.04.020.10422"},["b","10"],"¶And the man that committeth adultery with",["i","another"],"man’s wife,",["i","even he"],"that committeth adultery with his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"neighbour’s"],"wife, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"adulterer"],"and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"adulteress"],"shall surely be put to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.11","order":"02.04.020.10423"},["b","11"],"And the man that lieth with his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"father’s"],"wife hath uncovered his father’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"nakedness"],": both of them shall surely be put to death; their blood",["i","shall be"],"upon them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.12","order":"02.04.020.10424"},["b","12"],"And if a man lie with his daughter in law, both of them shall surely be put to death: they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"wrought confusion"],"; their blood",["i","shall be"],"upon them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.13","order":"02.04.020.10425"},["b","13"],"If a man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"also lie with mankind"],", as he lieth with a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"woman"],", both of them have committed an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"abomination"],": they shall surely be put to death; their blood",["i","shall be"],"upon them."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.14","order":"02.04.020.10426"},["b","14"],"And if a man take a wife and her mother, it",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wickedness"],": they shall be burnt with fire, both he and they; that there be no wickedness among you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.15","order":"02.04.020.10427"},["b","15"],"And if a man lie with a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"beast"],", he shall surely be put to death: and ye shall slay the beast."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.16","order":"02.04.020.10428"},["b","16"],"And if a woman approach unto any beast, and lie down thereto, thou shalt kill the woman, and the beast: they shall surely be put to death; their blood",["i","shall be"],"upon them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.17","order":"02.04.020.10429"},["b","17"],"And if a man shall take his sister, his father’s daughter, or his mother’s daughter, and see her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"nakedness"],", and she see his nakedness; it",["i","is"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"wicked thing"],"; and they shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"cut off"],"in the sight of their people: he hath uncovered his sister’s nakedness; he shall bear his iniquity."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.18","order":"02.04.020.10430"},["b","18"],"And if a man shall lie with a woman having her sickness, and shall uncover her nakedness; he hath discovered her fountain, and she hath uncovered the fountain of her blood: and both of them shall be cut off from among their people."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.19","order":"02.04.020.10431"},["b","19"],"And thou shalt not uncover the nakedness of thy mother’s sister, nor of thy father’s sister: for he uncovereth his near kin: they shall bear their iniquity."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.20","order":"02.04.020.10432"},["b","20"],"And if a man shall lie with his uncle’s wife, he hath uncovered his uncle’s nakedness: they shall bear their sin; they shall die childless."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.21","order":"02.04.020.10433"},["b","21"],"And if a man shall take his brother’s wife, it",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"an unclean thing"],": he hath uncovered his brother’s nakedness; they shall be childless."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.22","order":"02.04.020.10434"},["b","22"],"¶Ye shall therefore keep all my statutes, and all my judgments, and do them: that the land, whither I bring you to dwell therein,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"spue"],"you not out."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.23","order":"02.04.020.10435"},["b","23"],"And ye shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"walk"],"in the manners of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"nation"],", which I cast out before you: for they committed all these things, and therefore I abhorred them."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.24","order":"02.04.020.10436"},["b","24"],"But I have said unto you, Ye shall inherit their land, and I will give it unto you to possess it, a land that floweth with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"milk"],"and honey: I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, which have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"separated"],"you from",["i","other"],"people."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.25","order":"02.04.020.10437"},["b","25"],"Ye shall therefore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"put difference between"],"clean beasts and unclean, and between unclean fowls and clean: and ye shall not make your souls abominable by beast, or by fowl, or by any manner of living thing that creepeth on the ground, which I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"separated"],"from you as",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.26","order":"02.04.020.10438"},["b","26"],"And ye shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"holy"],"unto me: for I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","am"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"holy"],", and have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"severed"],"you from",["i","other"],"people, that ye should be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_26d"},"mine"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.27","order":"02.04.020.10439"},["b","27"],"¶A man also or woman that hath a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"familiar spirit"],", or that is a wizard, shall surely be put to death: they shall stone them with stones: their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"blood"],["i","shall be"],"upon them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.2a","order":"02.04.020.10440"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.3a","order":"02.04.020.10442"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.3b","order":"02.04.020.10444"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"TG Profanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.4a","order":"02.04.020.10446"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.5.2-3,5"},"Deut. 17:5 (2–3, 5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.5a","order":"02.04.020.10448"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/21.10"},"Jer. 21:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.11"},"44:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.5b","order":"02.04.020.10450"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.9.8-9"},"Jer. 3:9 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/23.37"},"Ezek. 23:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6a","order":"02.04.020.10452"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"to magic or necromancy."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6b","order":"02.04.020.10454"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6c","order":"02.04.020.10456"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6d","order":"02.04.020.10458"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.19"},"2 Ne. 18:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.6e","order":"02.04.020.10460"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/excommunication"},"TG Excommunication"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.7a","order":"02.04.020.10462"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/21.8"},"Lev. 21:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.32"},"22:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.74"},"D&C 88:74"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.7b","order":"02.04.020.10464"},["b","7b"],["span.small","OR"],"saints."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.8a","order":"02.04.020.10466"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/19.3"},"Lev. 19:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.9a","order":"02.04.020.10468"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.9b","order":"02.04.020.10470"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-duties-of"},"TG Family, Children, Duties of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.9c","order":"02.04.020.10472"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10a","order":"02.04.020.10474"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.11"},"Ezek. 18:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10b","order":"02.04.020.10476"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10c","order":"02.04.020.10478"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.5"},"John 8:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10d","order":"02.04.020.10480"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/capital-punishment"},"TG Capital Punishment"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.11a","order":"02.04.020.10482"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/22.30"},"Deut. 22:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.11b","order":"02.04.020.10484"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.8.7-8"},"Lev. 18:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.12a","order":"02.04.020.10486"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"done lewdness."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.13a","order":"02.04.020.10488"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"lies with a male."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.13b","order":"02.04.020.10490"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.13c","order":"02.04.020.10492"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/homosexual-behavior"},"TG Homosexual Behavior"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.14a","order":"02.04.020.10494"},["b","14a"],["span.small","OR"],"lewdness or an evil device."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.15a","order":"02.04.020.10496"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.21"},"Deut. 27:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.17a","order":"02.04.020.10498"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.22"},"Deut. 27:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.17b","order":"02.04.020.10500"},["b","17b"],["span.small","OR"],"disgrace (Aramaism)."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.17c","order":"02.04.020.10502"},["b","17c"],["span.small","IE"],"publicly excommunicated."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.21a","order":"02.04.020.10504"},["b","21a"],["span.small","HEB"],"impurity; i.e., repulsive.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.16"},"Lev. 18:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/14.4.3-4"},"Matt. 14:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.22a","order":"02.04.020.10506"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.38.37-38"},"1 Ne. 17:38 (37–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.23a","order":"02.04.020.10508"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.23b","order":"02.04.020.10510"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/7.1.1-2"},"Deut. 7:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.24a","order":"02.04.020.10512"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.18"},"D&C 38:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.24b","order":"02.04.020.10514"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.53"},"1 Kgs. 8:53"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.25a","order":"02.04.020.10516"},["b","25a"],["span.small","HEB"],"distinguish between."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.25b","order":"02.04.020.10518"},["b","25b"],["span.small","HEB"],"distinguished for you as impure."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.25c","order":"02.04.020.10520"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.15"},"Acts 10:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.26a","order":"02.04.020.10522"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peculiar-people"},"TG Peculiar People"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.26b","order":"02.04.020.10524"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.26c","order":"02.04.020.10526"},["b","26c"],["span.small","HEB"],"distinguished you from the nations.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/separation"},"TG Separation"],"."],["div",{"id":"26d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.26d","order":"02.04.020.10528"},["b","26d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/24.17"},"3 Ne. 24:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.27a","order":"02.04.020.10530"},["b","27a"],"This is in Hebrew",["span.translit",["span.emphasis","ov,"]],"a skin bottle used as an instrument of necromancy.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.27b","order":"02.04.020.10532"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/1.19"},"Jacob 1:19"],"."]]}
